Project Overview
This project demonstrates a complete CI/CD pipeline for a Node.js application using Jenkins and Docker deployed on AWS EC2
The pipeline automatically builds and deploys the application whenever code is pushed to GitHub.

Architecture



The application follows the below architecture:

Developer pushes code to GitHub

Jenkins automatically triggers pipeline

Docker image is built

Old container is stopped

New container is deployed

Application is accessible via EC2 public IP

